These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, scooter, motorbike
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Transport   | motorbike | scooter | trike |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, aconite
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, tram, van
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growspoppy is somewhere between the person who growsaconite and the person driving the tram##7
3. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Flower   | daisy | poppy | aconite |
| Transport     | tram       | van     | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, sports, animation
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, train
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre    | spy | sports | animation  |
| Transport   | train  | subway  | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, gardening, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, comedy, time-travel
1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
2. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Hobby           | gardening | singing | skydiving     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | action          | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, salsa
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, chinese
1. the dutch is somewhere between the chinese and the fan of hip-hop##7
2. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | salsa     | hip-hop   |
| Nationality     | chinese | dutch | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, jazz, reggae
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, ivory, red
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
2. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who likes red##1
4. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the person who likes red and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | jazz     | blues     |
| Color   | red | ivory | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia, apricot
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the person who's sport is badminton##7
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Color     | apricot       | fuchsia      | orange       |
| Sport   | badminton | skateboarding | basketball |

