2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person drinking 7up##7
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage           | fanta | hot-chocolate  | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery | sports      |

