2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | writing | chess   |
| Transport     | roller    | subway  | motorbike |

