.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
House: art-deco, modern, futuristic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, tennis
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the modern house##1
3. the futuristic house is somewhere between the modern house and the person who's sport is skiing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House   | modern   | futuristic    | art-deco |
| Sport      | tennis | badminton | skiing |

