.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo, cycling
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, german, thai
1. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the german and the dutch##7
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the dutch is not the person who's sport is cycling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Sport         | cycling | swimming | water-polo |
| Nationality   | german    | thai    | dutch         |

