.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, lawyer, entrepreneur
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, zombie
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the musician##7
3. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Job          | musician  | entrepreneur       | lawyer     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific | superhero |

