.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, backgammon
1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing backgammon##7
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | coffee     | iced-tea | cola |
| Game   | mah-jongg | monopoly    | backgammon |

