.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, banana, watermelon
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, electrician
1. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
2. the electrician is the person eating banana##1
3. the lawyer is somewhere between the electrician and the person eating artichoke##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | banana | watermelon | artichoke |
| Job   | electrician  | lawyer       | fisherman      |

