.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-15::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, september, august
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's sport is swimming##7
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday     | august  | may       | september    |
| Sport   | cricket | water-polo | swimming |

