.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, peach, potato
3 different games are played: canasta, chess, monopoly
1. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
2. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person playing canasta##7
4. the person playing canasta is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato | peach     | avocado   |
| Game   | monopoly   | chess | canasta |

