.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, trance, electronic
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the fan of trance##7
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | tea     | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre        | electronic | metal | trance    |

 